							<a href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AThe Destructive Legacy of Failed Aquaculture%0D%0ARemoving abandoned infrastructure is challenging, time-consuming, and costly.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/the-destructive-legacy-of-failed-aquaculture/" title="Share by Email" target="_blank">
